AiSummaryContaineruniface_104ytp1665702673217.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytp1665702673217.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ytp1665702673217.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ytp1665702673217\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies the host identifier of the machine where the Uniface Debugger is\n      located.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__topic_d145127e1_d145128e1_d145129e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__p_d145130e1_d145131e1_d145132e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">UDBG_Machine</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">localhost</code> | <var class=\"keyword varname\">HostID</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__section_w3150ab1b5b3_w3151ab1b5_w3152ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__p_d145133e1_d145134e1_d145135e1\">For example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">udbg_machine=localhost</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">udbg_machine=127.0.0.1</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__section_zpd_xfp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d455653e80\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__p_d145139e1_d145140e1_d145141e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">HostID</var> is the network node name for the machine, for example\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">AMS093606.uniface.emea</code> or <code class=\"ph codeph\">127.0.0.1</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ytp1665702673217__table_d17666e1_d17667e1_d17668e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">localhost</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efz1665702672861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efz1665702672861.html\" title=\"The [install] section of the initialization file contains information about the current installation.\">[install]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534261\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534261\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UDBG_Machine Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies the host identifier of the machine where the Uniface Debugger is located. UDBG_Machine = localhost | HostID For example: udbg_machine=localhost or udbg_machine=127.0.0.1 Arguments HostID is the network node name for the machine, for example AMS093606.uniface.emea or 127.0.0.1 . Default value: localhost File section: [install] Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}